<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Falconridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community in Falconridge is one of the most desirable neighborhoods among others, given its centralized location within the city. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">From schools to large well-maintained parks, shopping malls and sports venues, the community offers a myriad of quality recreational services and public amenities for its residents to lead a relaxed and comfortable life.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The Falconridge real estate offers a variety of housing options for its future residents ranging from detached townhomes, row houses to apartments and condominiums that are typically listed at an average price of $320,000.</p>
        </div>
